John McNertney, CFP®, Director
 
John is a Director and a member of the Business Development Team with Polaris Greystone. John has extensive experience within the financial services industry, having worked at TD Ameritrade and Merrill Lynch prior to joining the Polaris Greystone team.  John meets directly with clients and prospective clients to communicate Polaris Greystone's investment strategies and review all financial planning needs.
 
John is a graduate of the University of Iowa, where he earned a BS degree with a major in psychology and minors in French and philosophy. He is also a Certified Financial Planner™ professional. John possesses an in-depth knowledge of the financial markets and prides himself on delivering a world-class experience to our clients.
 
When he is not helping clients, John is an avid family man, spending his free time with his wife and three children. He is a voracious reader and enjoys watching news programs and documentaries. 
 
Polaris Greystone Financial Group, LLC is an independently owned, Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) Registered Investment Adviser.  We are a fee-only adviser and do not charge commissions for buying or selling stocks or bonds. Our services include: tactical portfolio management, private wealth management and financial planning… all provided with unparalleled individual attention focused on developing successful, long-term relationship.





