MISSION. VISION. VALUES.
A MESSAGE FROM OUR PRINCIPALS








 


Mission. Vision. Values.
Our Difference
Our Team
Careers


 
MISSION
Our mission is to provide a financial oasis for investors seeking:

investments and fees that are completely transparent;
to work with a trusted advisor whom they can share all of their hopes and dreams; and
to work with a firm they can trust to delegate the responsibilities needed to help them accomplish their long-term financial goals.

We believe that proper communication is the cornerstone to any good relationship. This begins by listening to our clients. We are committed to understanding each of our client’s individual needs and to creating a realistic plan to help accomplish their long-term goals. We are committed to communicating the complexities of the financial industry in easy-to-understand terms and to keeping our clients informed about the markets and their portfolio throughout the year.
We are relentless in our effort to understand the markets, their inherent risks, and to managing our portfolio strategies responsibly based upon this knowledge. It is our job to navigate these complexities in order to help our clients safely reach their long-term financial goals. 
 
 
 


VISION
 
GLOBAL PERSPECTIVE
You need a firm that understands what’s going on in the world and how it affects your financial objectives.
 
NATIONAL PRESENCE
With offices in some of the nation’s largest metropolitan areas, we’re there for you when you need us.
 
PERSONAL GUIDANCE
We provide the personal attention of a boutique firm with the comprehensive resources of a large firm.
 
 
VALUES
 
OBJECTIVITY
We are fiduciary, and advise carefully in order to act in your best interest.
We actually work for you. 
 
TRANSPARENCY
We are a fee-only federally registered investment adviser.
Our interests = your interests.
 
LONG-TERM PLANNING
We create wealth management plans that go beyond your needs today.
We can't know what will happen tomorrow, but we like to be prepared for what might.




JEFFREY POWELL
Founder & Managing Partner,
Polaris Greystone Financial Group
Jeff's Bio »


TODD MOSS, CFP®
